quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,59,"Ha…óaali Men nde Men nula Aayeeje …óen, si wanaa sabu fenniino …óe adii…ďe …ďen, Men okki Samuuda Naaqaawa mban yi'teemba …ďe too√Īi mba, Men nuliraali Aayeeje …óen si wonaa hul…ďinir…óe"
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde Men wi'anno maa: \"Pellet, Joomi maa O hu…ďindike yim…ďe …ďen, Men wa…óiraali nden yi'annde nde Men hollumaa si wanaa fitina wonannde yim…ďe …ďen e lekki hu…óaaki ki ka Alqur'aana, Me…óen hul…ďina …ďe kono …ďeydataa …ďe si wanaa bewre mawnde"
  17,61,"Nde Men Daalannoo Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen sujjanee Aadama, …ďe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o wi'i: \"Hara mi sujjanay on mo tagu∆äaa e loopal"
  17,62,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii oo mo teddin∆äaa e dow an, pellet, si A nennanii lan haa √Īalde darngal mi bonnay …ďi…ď…ďe makko …ďen si wanaa see…óaa…ďe"
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: \"Yahu, kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ď…ďe pellet, ko jahannama woni njoddi mon, njoddi yonoori"
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo hattana…óaa e ma…ď…ďe hito maa ngon, poo…óu e dow ma…ď…ďe pucci maa e seppoo…ďe maa, ka fidu e ma…ď…ďe ka jawle e ka …ďi…ď…ďe fodu…ďe, [kono] Seytaane fodaali …ďe si wanaa hodo"
  17,65,"Pellet, Jeyaa…ďe An …ďen a maraa doole e hoore ma…ď…ďe, Joomi maa yonii Hooloraa…óo"
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganay…óo on laa…óe …óen ka maayo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu immorde e …ďural Makko ngal, pellet, Kanko ko O Yurmetee…óo on"
